1. *Kasniš* već pola sata. (You're late for half an hour already.)
2. Izvinite, *kasnim* 10 minuta. (Sorry, I'm 10 minutes late.)
3. Čekamo te, *ne kasni!* (We're waiting for you, don't be late!)
4. Da li je moguće da *kasniš* i danas? (Is it possible that you're late again today?)
5. Molim te, javi mi ako ćeš *kasniti*. (Please let me know if you're going to be late.)
6. Nemoj da *kasniš* na važan sastanak. (Don't be late for an important meeting.)
7. Danas nećemo *kasniti*, voz kreće u 8 sati. (We won't be late today, the train leaves at 8 o'clock.)
8. *Kasniš* za poslednjim autobusom, moraćeš da čekaš sledeći. (You're late for the last bus, you'll have to wait for the next one.)
9. Ako *kasniš*, propuštaš priliku. (If you're late, you're missing an opportunity.)
10. Uvek *kasniš*, moraš da povedeš više računa o vremenu. (You're always late, you need to be more careful with time.)

Note: The star (*) is not used in the Serbian language to highlight a word, it is only used here to fulfill the requirement of the task.